                                                                                                <b>Otto Feuer</b>
                    <p class="utterance">Well, it . . . it . . . it&#39;s . . . I don&#39;t seem to . . . anybody will . . . will understand . . . it . . . our general feeling, why those Jews . . . why I every . . . most of the other Jews won&#39;t stay in Germany . . . Won&#39;t stay in Poland, that&#39;s we can no more see these people, it&#39;s too much for our memory, for our [word not clear] it&#39;s too much.</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
